Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.29,0:01:53.17,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Ayukawa Saori (27)\NTournament Participant
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.30,0:01:55.38,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Masubuchi Takuya (29)\NTournament Participant
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.55,0:01:57.51,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Funaki Toshihiko (35)\NFreelance Writer
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.73,0:02:57.40,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,THE FISHING TOURNAMENT TRAGEDY (PART TWO)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.15,0:02:59.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First, Masubuchi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.49,0:03:05.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please tell us your whereabouts between 10:00 and 10:30 AM yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.66,0:03:08.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,10:00 to 10:30, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.58,0:03:11.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was below the metal bridge at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.75,0:03:14.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which side of the metal bridge were you under?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.00,0:03:15.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The side with the rail tracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.05,0:03:17.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the tracks?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.17,0:03:19.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.09,0:03:23.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The location of Funaki's death is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.22,0:03:26.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the grass, 100 meters upstream from the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.72,0:03:29.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I figured as much...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.27,0:03:32.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was surprised to see so many police officers around there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.98,0:03:38.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I believe that the route to that area will pass by your backside...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.44,0:03:41.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you see anyone suspicious passing by?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.45,0:03:44.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I didn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.20,0:03:45.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was concentrating on my fishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.24,0:03:50.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is there anyone who can prove that you didn't leave the area below the bridge?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.50,0:03:51.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.46,0:03:53.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No solid alibi...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.00,0:03:56.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Masubuchi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was nearby...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.04,0:03:57.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.88,0:03:59.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.05,0:04:00.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that all?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.92,0:04:04.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, there's nothing else for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.39,0:04:15.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No sign that the victim called for help...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.35,0:04:16.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And no trace of the weapon used.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.94,0:04:21.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan, does this mean we can't fish anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.57,0:04:23.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It won't end this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.45,0:04:25.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You guys can still go fishing if you want to...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.79,0:04:30.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.79,0:04:34.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector, all the people on the lake were using rented boats...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.50,0:04:36.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And all of their alibis have just been confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.96,0:04:39.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems that there was never any boat near the crime scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.34,0:04:42.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So the culprit didn't use a boat?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.22,0:04:43.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.26,0:04:48.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then the culprit's probably among the people who walked around the lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.73,0:04:56.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector, we went to the hotel where the victim stayed last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.31,0:04:58.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And one guest was able to give us a valuable statement.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.23,0:05:00.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.40,0:05:01.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.44,0:05:05.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Apparently, the victim had some sort of dispute with a man named Masubuchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.82,0:05:06.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.07,0:05:07.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.62,0:05:15.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.50,0:05:17.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You seemed to have some sort of conflict with Funaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.29,0:05:19.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.46,0:05:20.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are you trying to eavesdrop here!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.71,0:05:22.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're just fishing here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.80,0:05:26.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we figure that we can catch some pretty big fish...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.55,0:05:29.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we're at the location selected by the front-runner, Masubuchi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.10,0:05:31.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, as big as a whale!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.31,0:05:34.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But we wouldn't be able to transport a fish that big!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.89,0:05:35.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.39,0:05:39.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Catching something like that would be perfect for showing off at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.81,0:05:40.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can show off!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.44,0:05:43.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, such big talk from such little kids...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.86,0:05:46.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, how about it, Masubuchi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.99,0:05:51.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Staying silent will only make your situation worse, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.62,0:05:55.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because many people witnessed your argument with Funaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.46,0:05:57.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Funaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.79,0:05:58.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Funaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.33,0:06:02.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I only raised my voice because...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.04,0:06:04.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said something odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.42,0:06:05.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something odd?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.80,0:06:07.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.97,0:06:09.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.59,0:06:12.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He asked, "You like Ayukawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, don't you?"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.85,0:06:16.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"If so, how about I take a picture of you with her?"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.44,0:06:18.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I got mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.10,0:06:21.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that the whole story?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.40,0:06:27.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and he said that she wouldn't be able to refuse if he told her to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.90,0:06:30.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Funaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} said that Ayukawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} wouldn't be able to refuse if he told her to do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.66,0:06:33.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.66,0:06:35.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayukawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} agreed to his request despite appearing unwilling...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.71,0:06:44.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone died here half a year ago as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.55,0:06:47.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan, why did we have to come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.67,0:06:50.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The police found nothing, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.76,0:06:53.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't think we can find any clues here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.39,0:06:54.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.22,0:06:56.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mitsuhiko has a point...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.97,0:06:58.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no murder weapon here...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.98,0:07:01.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And we didn't even hear a cry for help from Funaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.25,0:07:22.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Express train...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.80,0:07:27.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The smell of petroleum...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.17,0:07:28.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The stain on his vest...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.17,0:07:29.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.34,0:07:32.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta, Mitsuhiko—follow this track!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.51,0:07:33.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.93,0:07:36.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Funaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} wasn't killed here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.22,0:07:41.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He should've been killed somewhere along this track.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.19,0:07:49.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where are we going? I don't see anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.49,0:07:51.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're almost at Okutani Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.32,0:07:53.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There has to be something...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.32,0:07:56.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Getting hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.88,0:08:07.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doesn't that belong to Funaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.21,0:08:10.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the actual crime scene...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.67,0:08:11.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But how did the culprit do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.97,0:08:23.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did anyone come up to this bridge from 10:00 to 10:30 this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.44,0:08:26.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was there a photographer?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.19,0:08:29.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, he came at about 9:50 AM from the around the dam...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.94,0:08:32.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then left using the stairs that you guys just walked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.32,0:08:35.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did anybody else come here afterwards?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.16,0:08:40.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nobody else came after the scene caused by the arrival of all the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.20,0:08:41.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.70,0:08:44.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, Ayukawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} came early in the morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.62,0:08:45.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then left through those stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.17,0:08:47.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayukawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} did?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.84,0:08:50.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, at around 7:30...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.50,0:08:52.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She returned after about 10 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.14,0:09:00.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it was Ayukawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.06,0:09:03.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But how did she do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.98,0:09:06.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.35,0:09:09.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We almost forgot that we have to return the boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.77,0:09:14.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta, you said that you saw Ayukawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} walking upstream this morning, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.82,0:09:15.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which side of the shore was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.74,0:09:16.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.16,0:09:21.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was left from where we looked up...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.83,0:09:24.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it should be this side.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.16,0:09:27.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If she came back this way...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.42,0:09:30.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And threw a rock on Funaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} from above...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.96,0:09:33.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then she had to have crossed the bridge...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.01,0:09:37.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the guard said that nobody crossed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.89,0:09:43.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, if he was murdered here, how did the body end up all the way over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.60,0:09:45.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How did she carry it over?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.06,0:09:50.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he drifted naturally down the lake in that direction...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.48,0:09:53.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then crawled up onto shore after regaining consciousness...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.99,0:09:59.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, Funaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s body wasn't wet, and there was no boat involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.53,0:10:04.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Discovering the body over there simply feels unusual...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.29,0:10:07.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there's no doubt that this is the crime scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.75,0:10:08.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.21,0:10:12.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll be charged extra if we don't go return the boat now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.50,0:10:15.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How did the culprit do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.51,0:10:16.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, the boat...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.68,0:10:19.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I got it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.97,0:10:21.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you two getting on too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.60,0:10:22.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.51,0:10:23.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.85,0:10:31.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, let's get rid of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.11,0:10:32.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.48,0:10:34.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We found it earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.32,0:10:36.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.49,0:10:39.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Around where Kutani River merges with the main river path.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.91,0:10:41.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, that handkerchief...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.37,0:10:43.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.58,0:10:46.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That handkerchief... It belongs to Ayukawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.87,0:10:50.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.09,0:11:03.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the winner, with a total catch of 30.5 kilograms of bass, is Masubuchi Takuya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.72,0:11:10.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The sponsor's representative, Suzuki Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} will present the award.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.56,0:11:12.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's all give a round of applause!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.11,0:11:14.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A few words?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.15,0:11:17.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I chose the right location this time, and I got lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.03,0:11:19.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll put even more effort in the next tournament!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.74,0:11:23.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know you're the culprit—I'll find proof...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.87,0:11:29.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In second place, with a total catch of 22.68 kilograms, is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.33,0:11:30.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayukawa Saori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.71,0:11:35.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please share a few words!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.13,0:11:36.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I aimed for two wins in a row, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.30,0:11:39.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, I lost to Masubuchi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.55,0:11:43.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next year, I'll be the one taking home the big trophy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.47,0:11:47.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's give them another big round of applause!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.89,0:11:54.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, that concludes the 17th Suzuki Cup Lake Okutani Fishing Tournament!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.98,0:11:56.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you all for attending!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.11,0:12:06.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, doesn't that look a lot like Sleeping Kogorou!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.24,0:12:06.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.16,0:12:09.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayukawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, just a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.50,0:12:13.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd like for you to speak a little more...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.92,0:12:15.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About your motive for murdering Funaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.67,0:12:18.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.05,0:12:20.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? It was Ayukawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.63,0:12:24.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did something like this happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.72,0:12:26.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In this tournament sponsored by father's company?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.35,0:12:29.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, would you care to explain?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.85,0:12:32.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you saying!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.60,0:12:34.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At the time of the crime...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.19,0:12:36.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was at Kutani River, on the opposite side of the lake!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.27,0:12:39.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That doesn't matter...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.32,0:12:43.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because Funaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was not killed where he was found.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.36,0:12:45.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How is that possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.91,0:12:48.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, show it to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.45,0:12:54.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This camera was found by the rail track along the Kutani River.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.29,0:12:56.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It belongs to Funaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.50,0:13:00.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I remember it from when he took pictures of us yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.00,0:13:00.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.63,0:13:03.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The victim's camera was by the shore of Kutani River...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.68,0:13:06.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why was it there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.09,0:13:08.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The precise location is below the Kutani Bridge...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.47,0:13:13.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And these are the pictures developed from the film in the camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.18,0:13:14.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.86,0:13:24.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There is a picture of the express train among them, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.40,0:13:27.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only place to take a picture of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.74,0:13:33.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is the little piece of flatland underneath the Kutani Bridge where the frame and the cliff connect.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.58,0:13:37.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I asked the people working for the railroad magazine...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.37,0:13:41.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And they agreed that that place is the best location to take a good picture of the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.84,0:13:48.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayukawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, you were invited to have a drink with Funaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} last night, were you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.26,0:13:55.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,During that time, you heard that he wanted to photograph the express train for the magazine...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.35,0:13:56.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you informed him of that place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.98,0:13:58.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.02,0:14:02.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Funaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was found 3 kilometers away, on the other side of the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.36,0:14:06.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't I already tell you that that's irrelevant?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.32,0:14:08.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Yokomizo...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.07,0:14:13.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you notice the stain on Funaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s vest?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.33,0:14:16.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.21,0:14:20.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I suppose the forensics report did mention that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.21,0:14:22.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I believe it was petroleum and coal dust.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.80,0:14:27.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They were from the smoke expelled by the passing express train.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.63,0:14:28.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Smoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.26,0:14:31.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Funaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} had been on top of the express train...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.85,0:14:35.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From underneath the Kutani Bridge to the location his body was discovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.52,0:14:38.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On top of it!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.31,0:14:45.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While waiting for the best opportunity for a good shot of the train...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.57,0:14:51.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Funaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was struck on the head by a falling rock...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.12,0:14:53.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And fell over the cliff onto the top of the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.28,0:14:56.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After that, he stayed up there and passed the bridge...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.50,0:14:58.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fell off when the train made a sharp turn...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.46,0:15:00.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And landed where we found him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.25,0:15:04.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But isn't all that a little too much of a coincidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.92,0:15:06.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.55,0:15:09.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A train leaves the Okutani Station every morning at 10:50.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.26,0:15:12.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In order to make sure that he fell onto the train...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.14,0:15:15.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayukawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} needed perfect timing to kill Funaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.72,0:15:18.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.68,0:15:22.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was the location that the body fell to also a part of her calculations?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.19,0:15:23.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Most likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.44,0:15:24.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.69,0:15:26.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No matter how careless Funaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.65,0:15:30.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It couldn't have been that easy for Saori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.95,0:15:31.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.57,0:15:34.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it's something like a rock that's thrown down from the bridge...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.16,0:15:38.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The guard at the end of the bridge should've seen it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.45,0:15:41.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have confirmed with the guard...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.17,0:15:46.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That nobody crossed the bridge between 10:00 and 10:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.55,0:15:49.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, then Saori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} couldn't possibly have committed the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.26,0:15:52.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've been made to think that way...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.89,0:15:55.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Saori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} is indeed the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.47,0:15:58.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a very meticulously planned-out and executed crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.64,0:15:59.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.48,0:16:04.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was at Kutani River, on the other side of the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.94,0:16:07.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Weren't you, Saori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.69,0:16:08.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.78,0:16:10.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But what the guard said...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.86,0:16:16.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was that Ayukawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} walked down the nearby stairs at 7:30 AM.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.95,0:16:21.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even so, I don't think her going there at that time has anything to do with the crime...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.62,0:16:22.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.96,0:16:24.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.67,0:16:28.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't this just a wooden board?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.30,0:16:34.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} and Mitsuhiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} found this while on their boat...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.18,0:16:38.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At the location where the Kutani River merges into the main one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.56,0:16:41.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayukawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} used this board there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.93,0:16:42.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How did she use it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.48,0:16:45.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At around 7:30 in the morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.36,0:16:49.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayukawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} tied the board directly above where Funaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} stood...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.53,0:16:55.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With half of it dangling in the air, just on the verge of falling over...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.61,0:16:57.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And placed a rock on top of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.12,0:17:05.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At 10:07, from the other side of the bridge...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.92,0:17:09.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayukawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} aimed her fishing hook above Funaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, who was taking photos of the train...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.32,0:17:36.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's just what you imagined...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.74,0:17:38.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you have any actual proof that this happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.20,0:17:44.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Masubuchi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, didn't you find it odd that Ayukawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} would go to Kutani River?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.71,0:17:48.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not a very good fishing spot, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.54,0:17:52.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, why would she be there if her goal was to win first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.09,0:17:58.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, the handkerchief tied to the board belongs to her, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.80,0:18:01.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyone could have the same kind of handkerchief!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.31,0:18:04.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please go analyze that handkerchief...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.60,0:18:06.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It should react to luminol.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.39,0:18:08.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I don't see any bloodstains on it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.27,0:18:15.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayukawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, didn't you use this handkerchief when Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} hurt herself yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.32,0:18:20.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, some of her blood has to be on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.45,0:18:24.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, you won't be able to see it now...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.87,0:18:26.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, Ayukawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.37,0:18:28.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After drying once...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.79,0:18:33.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Blood will react to luminol no matter how much you wash it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.80,0:18:38.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just how long after helping Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} did you wash it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.55,0:18:40.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayukawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.80,0:18:42.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did you murder Funaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.02,0:18:48.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For half a year, that guy's been blackmailing me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.60,0:18:51.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.15,0:18:53.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Half a year ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.57,0:18:56.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A person named Kanie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} also wound up like Funaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.99,0:18:58.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And was discovered at the same location.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.41,0:19:04.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Funaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s blackmail probably has something to do with that incident, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.74,0:19:08.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I never intended to kill Kanie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.91,0:19:11.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean that you killed this man named Kanie too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.25,0:19:15.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were walking along Kutani River...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.13,0:19:19.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm just not ready for marriage yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.01,0:19:22.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're in love with Masubuchi after all, aren't you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.72,0:19:27.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How about it? At least give me a clear answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.23,0:19:30.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.15,0:19:38.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So Funaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} happened to witness that incident...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.44,0:19:41.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then threatened you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.41,0:19:44.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.20,0:19:50.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I won't mention anything to the police...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.08,0:19:54.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In exchange, you help me financially. I'm in a pinch and could use 2 million yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.67,0:19:55.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.09,0:20:05.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The newest camera on the market costs over a million yen...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.18,0:20:05.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.39,0:20:11.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On three different occasions...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.27,0:20:13.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I actually gave him more than 7 million yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.36,0:20:17.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then, about half a month ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.73,0:20:22.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard about how you got sponsored by Pacific Sports, with a contract and everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.03,0:20:25.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How much are you raking in?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.41,0:20:27.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.53,0:20:28.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whatever you say...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.83,0:20:31.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Think you can toss me 10 million yen?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.12,0:20:34.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If not, you know what would happen, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.96,0:20:41.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After that, when he mentioned that he wanted to photograph that express train...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.05,0:20:45.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought he would definitely go to that spot below the bridge if I told him about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.97,0:20:47.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All you had to do was get the timing right...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.80,0:20:49.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the train would just carry the body away...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.89,0:20:52.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Exactly how it happened with Kanie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.19,0:20:54.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was your plan, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.27,0:20:58.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I thought about the possibility of being blackmailed for the rest of my life...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.90,0:21:01.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It would make my sight turn completely black...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.57,0:21:05.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems I've ruined your whole tournament...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.32,0:21:06.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I truly am sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.24,0:21:11.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Compared to me, isn't the tournament more important to people like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.59,0:21:19.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.00,0:21:21.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.22,0:21:27.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayukawa Saori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, we'll have to discuss the case in further detail...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.64,0:21:28.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please come with us to the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.93,0:21:30.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.68,0:21:34.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.27,0:21:39.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No matter how long it takes, I'll be waiting for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.94,0:21:40.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.20,0:23:12.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They really were amazing, weren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.28,0:23:14.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}'s deductions.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.24,0:23:15.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They sure were!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.79,0:23:19.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seriously, when did you go investigate all of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.58,0:23:22.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, uhm, little by little...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.42,0:23:23.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a piece of cake for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.21,0:23:26.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't remember anything about doing something that great...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.09,0:23:28.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this "little by little" stuff about...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.18,0:23:33.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, what about you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.18,0:23:34.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Catch any fish?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.10,0:23:36.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, that...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.10,0:23:41.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Making a big catch is way harder than solving a case...
